Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa ahhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't all\Nhave magical horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to\Nmove these older books
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to my "reference"\Nsection for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta keep the new\Nbooks front and center!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both for\Nyour help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? After\Nall you've done for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the least\NI can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, I haven't\Ndone that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. You just taught me\Nthe value of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have offered\Nsome guidance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are responsible\Nfor the pony you've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to call you my\Nstudent AND my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we just need to\Nget rid of these boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, can you... Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a parasprite?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's... INCOMING!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I usually get\Nletters by dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It IS the fastest\Nway to get mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For me? Who would be\Nsending me a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ponies\Nfrom my old village.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they upset with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They've invited me to the\Nannual sunset festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\NBy YayPonies\NThere wasn't even a muffin in that letter :/\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey there,\Neverypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Hey Starlight. What\Nare you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I was invited. To\Nthe Sunset Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh yeah. But we didn't think\Nyou'd actually show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't think we really\Nwanted you here did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I apologized. I thought\Neverything was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE. Stop. STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Is\Nanypony there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna? What\Nare you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams are my domain,\NStarlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here because\Nyou need me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It may only be a dream, but\Nthe feelings in it are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. So I guess\NI'm more afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of going back\Nto the village
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,than I thought.\NWhat do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been helped\Ntime and time again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,by six very\Nspecial ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They helped me\Novercome my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are fortunate to\Nhave them as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you share your\Nconcerns with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see much of myself in\Nyou, Starlight Glimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can tell you from\Npersonal experience
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that things do\Nindeed get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,... and Princess Luna\Nsaid I should tell you all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,how I was feeling.\NSo, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to go back to the\Nvillage for the celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But why, darling? You went back\Nto apologize; they accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony has moved on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But have they? They don't really\Nknow how much I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even worse, maybe I\Nhaven't changed as much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as I think I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,TRUST ME. You are a totally\Ndifferent pony now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...you were\Npretty awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,RAINBOW DASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?! She WAS!\NIt's a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they would\Nhave sent the invitation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if they didn't want\Nyou to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'd be\Nhappy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And getting an invitation\Nto a party and NOT GOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like...\Nit's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know what it's\Nlike, but it is definitely bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be honest\Nwith them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll understand\Nwhere you're comin' from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how\Nhard this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you took\Na friend along,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it might\Nmake things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony you trust who\Nwould look out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much for\Ndoing this, Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When Twilight said I\Nshould bring a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you were the first\Npony I thought of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea,\NPrincess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking me, Starlight's\NBEST friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to help her on this\Ndifficult journey
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,really shows how wise a\Nprincess you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was TALKING about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The festival lasts\Na whole week,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure we\Nwon't stay that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I don't know,\NStarlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,time really flies when\Nyou're spending it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with your BEST FRIEND!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye Starlight!See\Nyou later! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! The\Ntown where you --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Magically stole\Neverypony's cutie mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,replaced them with equal\Nsigns and forced them all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to hide their\Nnatural talents? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going say\Nwhere you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But yours is a more...\Nemotionally traumatic answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to blend in. Be\Njust another pony in the crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoying the Sunset\NFestival with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me. And if\Nthings get weird for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,just let me know.\NI've got your flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just a promise. A GREAT\Nand POWERFUL promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't ask\Nfor more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna do\Nthis, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! STARLIGHT! YOU CAME!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We were worried you\Nwouldn't be able to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you staying\Nthe whole week?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have different\Nevents planned each day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it living\Nin a castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is SO good\Nto see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. These ponies\Nare terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see\Nall of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You got here\NJUST in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We were having some debate\Nabout these banners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you think\Nfeels more sunsety?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't need\Nme to decide that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you think\Nis probably best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh well, how about\Nhelping us with the routes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for the relay races tomorrow.\NCan you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I shouldn't.\NYou all go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to\Nenjoy the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But you WILL be a judge for\Nthe baking competition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a few questions\Nabout the order of the acts
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for the talent show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the unicorns have a\Nfireworks show planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We could REALLY\Nuse your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The great and powerful Trixie\Nwould like to thank you all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for being such an\Namazing audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly it is time\Nfor us to depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, fillies\Nand gentlefoals!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. I was horrible\Nwhen I led that town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ready for them to not\Ntrust me, but I wasn't ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for them to put me\Nin charge again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With my past, I should never\Nbe in charge of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you messed\Nup. Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever tell\Nanother pony I said this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but even Trixie's made\Nmistakes. Ha, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick is to just move on and\Npretend they never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like that's\Nalmost good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Uh, Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So. You're probably wondering\Nwhy I'm back so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to my old village?\NFor the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo sounds fun!\NHow was it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was kind of a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back early\Nbecause I freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, sounds awful! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she always strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm back early!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome\Nback.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you two noticed Pinkie\Nacting a little strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie always\Nacts strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I wanted to\Ntalk to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Things didn't go the way I\Nthought they were going to go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Sunset Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of freaked out and\Nran out of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,HA HA HA!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You freaked out and ran\Naway from a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! That's the funniest dang\Nthing I've heard all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha, Oh my! Let me guess. The\Ndecorations were TERRIFYING!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,HA HA HA!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello ponies. We need\NRarity and Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Very important\Nfriendship business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say I'm really not\Nas impressed with your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as the rest of\NEquestria is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk\Nto Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?\NTwilight's very busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I really need\Nto speak with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Make an appointment! She's\Na princess after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?\NWhy are you being so--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rude? I think a certain dragon\Ndidn't get his nap today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah right. Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, he's been acting\Na little off all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he missed a\Nmeal or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the\Nonly one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony is acting a\Nlittle strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's definitely been one\Nof those days. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not great actually.\NYou're probably wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,why I'm back from the\Nvillage so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to bring it up but\Nyeah, it did seem strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it not go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The townsponies kept\Nasking me things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,like they expected me\Nto be in charge again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But being a leader is the\Nlast thing I should ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So we left. Very suddenly.\NIn a literal puff of smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You should DEFINITELY\Nnever go back to that village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were worried about what\Nthey thought of you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's probably WAY worse\Nnow. I'd cut my losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's surprising\Nadvice coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me. I'm the\NPrincess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need those ponies. You\Ncan always make more friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, speaking of friends,\Nif you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Important business to attend to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut my losses? That\Ncan't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I wanted to apologize\Nfor my behavior earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Party Favor? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I TOLD you, you can never\Nspeak to them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Making sure you do what I said!\NI'm your teacher,aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say to\Nnever come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but that's just\Ndoesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't acting like\Nyourself. Something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream! This is\Nanother dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Starlight Glimmer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Starlight Glimmer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,STARLIGHT GLIMMER!THERE IS\NNO TIME! YOU MUST GET HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking\Nabout? This is just a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,NOT HERE! IN THE WAKING WORLD!\NTHEY'VE TAKEN MY SISTER AND I!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,IT'S WORSE THAN THE LAST TIME!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUR DREAM CALLED TO ME AND\NI WAS ABLE TO BREAK THROUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU MUST FIND HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NWHO'S taken you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,BE CAREFUL WHO YOU TRUST.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU WILL NEED ALL THE\NHELP YOU CAN FIND.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CHANGELINGS\NHAVE RETURNED AND--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE BACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie? Trixie, it's\NStarlight! Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of COURSE Princess Celestia,\NI'd love to perform
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,for Peanut Butter crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,TRIXIE! WAKE UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight? What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late. I think I figured out\Nwhat's wrong with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a whole\Nlist of things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that are wrong\Nwith your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go over it\Nin the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Trixie, we're in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,OK fine. Aside from lack of\Nsleep, how are we in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you tell me never\Nto tell another pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, if you woke me\Nup to play guessing games--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After we left my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you tell me to never\Ntell another pony you said!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That even Trixie's\Nmade mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie, there's no time for\Nthis. What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That even Trixie's made\Nmistakes, OK? Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Sorry. I just had to make\Nsure you weren't one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One of who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they've taken Princess\NCelestia and Princess Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you sure? I\Nmean, what do we--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to tell Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm right, then it's\Ntoo late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,QUEEN CHRYSALIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't take\Nany of you seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,MUCH better. Now report.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything here is going\Naccording to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've replaced the six\Nponies and their dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and have taken\Ncontrol of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent. And I've\Njust received word
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Princesses from\NCanterlot have successfully
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,been replaced as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought too small last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ONE ponynapped\Nprincess wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With ALL the most beloved ponies\Nof Equestria taken care of,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,NOPONY can stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't deal with this.\NI'm just a performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... this is\Nprincess level stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But the changeling's have all of\Nthe princesses. We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not. Queen Chrysalis only\Nsaid they took Luna and Celestia
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and obviously Twilight\Nand the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe Cadance is still safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our best bet is to get\Nto the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,before the changelings\Ndo. That way we--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} There's no help coming{\i0}\N{\i1} from the Crystal Empire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorax?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wings look... different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I know you aren't\Nsome other changeling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending to be Throax?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there when Spike\Ndefended me to the ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Princess of Friendship,\NI should set an example
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of Equestria, but today,\Nit was Spike who taught me--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! OK. I believe you. We\Ndon't need the whole speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie, this is Thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a reformed changeling.\NHe's on our side, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, it's a pleasure to--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If Starlight says you're on\Nour side I believe her but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe just stay over\Nthere for now, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you mean\Nthere's no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the changelings\Nget Cadance too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They took Cadance, Shining\NArmor AND Flurry Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst sent me here to get\NPrincess Twilight's help
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but it sounds like it's\Ntoo late for that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Starlight what\Nare we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't know. There\Nhas to be somepony else
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is NOPONY else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony with powerful\Nmagic is already gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, whenever ponies\Ntalk about powerful magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they always leave me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I weren't so evolved, I might\Ndecide to take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't this\NQUITE the combination
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of secondary characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Twilight\Nand the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,First, how do we know\Nthat you're really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis and the\Nchangelings are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They've ponynapped all of\Nthe most powerful ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia, Luna, Cadance,\NShining Armor, Flurry Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight and her\Nfriends. We need to--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They took Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The changeling kingdom. With\Nyou on our side, I think we --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Odd. I was trying to take\Nus right to Fluttershy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is no Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have a pretty good\Nidea where she might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I'd hoped to never see\Nthat place again. Now what?
